  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To treat breast tumors in non surgical patients with percutaneous technique (radiofrequency).
      Prospective evaluation of treatment efficiency and tolerance based on clinical and
      radiological evaluation
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
